descriptionHtml:
NPR (aka KURUSE) is the author of these outfits. It is an adaptation of a mod Elder Scrolls 4 Oblivion. It is inspired from Soul Calibur IV. I tried to adapt it to Skyrim. I started in this field.

There is only one size for now.

To install it:

Copy the contents in the data directory of Skyrim.

In the game (console mode):

amy help 0

player.additem xxxxxxxx 1

xxxxxxx is the number for the clothing you want to install
author: AZE
